    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and power delivery to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor; the rear subframe has been reinforced to prevent floor-pan stress fractures, and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows light patina, the mechanical components\u2014including verified rod bearing clearances and a recently shimmed valve train\u2014ensure the 8,000 RPM redline is met with precision. This is a driver-focused example where performance-critical maintenance has been prioritized.",
